data.description: Selestian floorplan: exquisite kitchen offers range, m'wave, and dw, an ex-wide breakfast bar + dining area lg enough to seat 10 or more. Comfy living room w/ceiling fan, wood-burning fireplace & lg closet. Upstairs: a jumbo -sized Master suite, 2 more bedrooms that share a hall bath + a bonus room completes this ideal houseplan. Linen closet in both master & hall bath. 12x12 patio to enjoy quiet country living. Copeland Heights, a Smithbilt n'hood, located in Powell, is one of Knox County's favorite living spots! 5 minutes to I-75, close-by shopping, great schools, churches, major hospital, golf & Norris lake & fishing -just 20 minutes away. Amenities include pool, pavilion & playground all set to open Memorial Day. Also sidewalks for strolling & streelights to brighten. County taxes only
